
<h4 style="font-family:'Poppins';font-size:17px;color:#555">General <small>(These tools are available whenever verses are displayed.)</small></h4>
<div class="container">
	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-lexicons" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-language" title="Lexicons"></i> 
			<b>Lexicons:</b>
		</span> 
		When the <b>Link Keyed</b> is set to Strong's, words keyed to Strong's Concordance will be highlighted (<span style="color:#833;font-weight:600">in red</span>). Clicking the word will make the Strong's lexicon definition appear. (This is a dynamic action, which is triggered when you activate it once the page has loaded.)
	</p>
</div>

<h4 style="font-family:'Poppins';font-size:17px;color:#555">Reference Search <small>(These tools are available when performing a reference search. e.g. <a href="{$page_url}?keyword=john+3:16">John 3:16</a>)</small></h4>
<div class="container">
	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-holman" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-arrows-turn-to-dots" title="Cross Reference"></i> 
			<b>Holman Cross-Reference:</b>
		</span> 
		Linking 3,992 verses to 57,812 related verses. (Will be in the margin next to the text in reference searches)
	</p>
	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-introduction" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-door-open"></i>
			<b>Book Introductions:</b>
		</span> 
		General information about the specific book of the Bible, by John MacArthur. Provided by his ministry, <a href="https://www.gty.org" target="_blank">Grace to You</a> (Used by permission)
	</p>
	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-outline" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-list-ol"></i>
			<b>Book Outlines:</b>
		</span> 
		Outline of the specific book of the Bible, by John MacArthur. Provided by his ministry, <a href="https://www.gty.org" target="_blank">Grace to You</a> (Used by permission)
	</p>
	
	
	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-interlinear" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-globe" title="Interlinear Bible"></i> 
			<b>Interlinear Bible:</b>
		</span> 
		The Interlinar Hebrew/Greek text. It can be displayed alongside the English text, and the keyed words will be matched by highlighting the corresponding keyed word.
	</p>
</div>

<h4 style="font-family:'Poppins';font-size:17px;color:#555">Word Search <small>(These tools are available when performing a word search. e.g. <a href="{$page_url}?keyword=love">&ldquo;love&rdquo;</a>)</small></h4>
<div class="container">

	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-filter" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-filter"></i>
			<b>Word Filter:</b>
		</span> 
		This tool displays a list of all the sections used by the scope filter, with the number of occurences of the keyword in each, linked to the word search limited by that scope.
	</p>

	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-eastons" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-book" title="Cross Reference"></i> 
			<b>Easton&rsquo;s Bible Dictionary:</b>
		</span> 
		Easton&rsquo;s timeless Bible Dictionary with 3,963 entries. If the word you are searching for is in the dictionary, then it's definition will be displayed in this tool.
	</p>

	<p id="virtual-bible-splash-tools-lexicon-entries" class="fontcolor-medium">
		<span class="tools-p-header">
			<i class="fas fa-language"></i>
			<b>Lexicon Entries:</b>
		</span> 
		A list of all Strong's entries which are keyed to this key word. Clicking on the entry title in the right pane will highlight any verses in the left pane that use that specific Strong's entry.
	</p>
</div>
